{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"85c20ebc3d","title":"关于财政预算问题给林伯渠的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"79ab9333f4","index":1,"year":1941,"month":6,"day":15,"articleId":"85c20ebc3d"},{"id":"a4b4cb21e0","index":0,"year":1941,"month":6,"day":13,"articleId":"85c20ebc3d"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenji2","name":"毛泽东文集第二卷（1999）","internal":false,"official":true,"type":"pdf","author":"中央文献研究室","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives9/main/books/wenji2.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"wenji2":{"comments":[{"id":"3cc25308d3","publicationId":"wenji2","articleId":"85c20ebc3d","index":-1,"part_index":-1,"offset":-1,"text":"根据手稿刊印。"},{"id":"e5f8b97862","publicationId":"wenji2","articleId":"85c20ebc3d","index":1,"part_index":0,"offset":12,"text":"林伯渠，当时任陕甘宁边区政府主席。"},{"id":"189769a781","publicationId":"wenji2","articleId":"85c20ebc3d","index":2,"part_index":7,"offset":4,"text":"谢老，指谢觉哉，当时任中共中央西北局副书记、中共陕甘宁边区政府党团书记、陕甘宁边区政府秘书长。"},{"id":"43d82dcd39","publicationId":"wenji2","articleId":"85c20ebc3d","index":3,"part_index":11,"offset":139,"text":"指当时康生任部长的中共中央社会部。"}],"contents":[{"id":"2a7592c6c9","type":"title","text":"关于财政预算问题给林伯渠的信","index":0,"publicationId":"wenji2","articleId":"85c20ebc3d"},{"id":"e5f8b97862","type":"appellation","text":"林老：","index":1,"publicationId":"wenji2","articleId":"85c20ebc3d"},{"id":"189769a781","type":"paragraph","text":"预决算看了，今付还。","index":2,"publicationId":"wenji2","articleId":"85c20ebc3d"},{"id":"43d82dcd39","type":"paragraph","text":"此类情况，以后请随时通知我，我虽不能为你分忧，但人事调整方面可多少帮你的忙。","index":3,"publicationId":"wenji2","articleId":"85c20ebc3d"},{"id":"894b9ea87d","type":"paragraph","text":"今日所谈，系大政方针与人事政策，承你同意，以后必可办通。","index":4,"publicationId":"wenji2","articleId":"85c20ebc3d"},{"id":"4b16b684dc","type":"paragraph","text":"有两点还请注意：（一）凡必不可免之钱，予以慨允，使受者得所。将来要塌台，让他塌去（实际上不会塌的），此时不与","index":5,"publicationId":"wenji2","articleId":"85c20ebc3d"},{"id":"3c2b355695","type":"paragraph","text":"计较。其原则就是“必不可免”四字。弱小部分，予以扶助，亦包括在此原则内。（二）不管是中央的，军队的，地方的，一概包揽，为之统筹。军队不分国军、地方军（不立此名目），一概统筹。此次预算内无军队部分，以后请添进去。是否有当，还请卓酌。","index":6,"publicationId":"wenji2","articleId":"85c20ebc3d"},{"id":"53ab703c6e","type":"paragraph","text":"并致谢老。","index":7,"publicationId":"wenji2","articleId":"85c20ebc3d"},{"id":"38f9b54da6","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":8,"publicationId":"wenji2","articleId":"85c20ebc3d"},{"id":"59a8fee309","type":"paragraph","text":"六月十三日夜","index":9,"publicationId":"wenji2","articleId":"85c20ebc3d"},{"id":"84f3170190","type":"paragraph","text":"总之发展路线是完全正确的。","index":10,"publicationId":"wenji2","articleId":"85c20ebc3d"},{"id":"1ec1b9d03e","type":"paragraph","text":"又陈者：（一）追加预计，不可免的，因预先计划不可能，例如《解放日报》经费，在决定出报前没有人能预计者。故只能由你在预算中加重总预备费，尔后按需要（必不可免者）支用。（二）不必肯定边币只维持一千万，宜作千五百万之打算，较不束缚手足。（三）预计算中应把自力更生部分打进去，例如康生处月用57，000元，只支12，000元，自筹45，000元，要把此数也打进去。大概公支只三分之一，自筹占三分之二。预计算中遗落此种部分是不合实际的。因此须与党、政、军各部分的实际状况密切联系，了解其情形，方能算计。尤其是军。（四）商品货币流通量成正比例说，亦不宜坚持，宜估计到许多新条件，还待今后研究。如持之过坚，将来不准，有损信誉。以上各点，就感想所及，书备考虑。","index":11,"publicationId":"wenji2","articleId":"85c20ebc3d"},{"id":"44128ed1ed","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":12,"publicationId":"wenji2","articleId":"85c20ebc3d"},{"id":"6a1d447719","type":"paragraph","text":"六月十五日","index":13,"publicationId":"wenji2","articleId":"85c20ebc3d"}],"page":{"id":"717de8311c","publicationId":"wenji2","articleId":"85c20ebc3d","start":367,"end":368}}}},"__N_SSG":true}